	<section class="about-me" id="about-me">
		<div class="info">
			<h2>Hello!</h2>
			<p>
				Whilst waiting to sit for legal qualifying exams, I decided to pick up what Felicity Smoak
				always made look very cool: programming. What I thought would remain a fun hobby quickly
				turned into something I fell in love with. I love the continual learning opportunities that
				web development provides -- there's always something cool that I have yet to master. I'm
				also confident that tech is the way forward in helping everyday people.
			</p>
		</div>
		<div class="pic-container">
			<img class="pic" src="src/lib/assets/dp.png" alt="Sonia William's animated headshot" />
		</div>
	</section>
